## CONTENT & COPY

- Write real, meaningful placeholder copy — not "Lorem ipsum" filler.
- Copy should reflect the actual industry and purpose of the site.
- Headlines must be punchy, benefit-led, and appropriate to the brand tone.
- Include realistic data in demos (real-looking names, prices, dates, stats).

